EMAIL_NOQ_SEBEBE_LONG_EN_LEGAL = "I was told I couldn’t apply for a room until 60 days in advance of the event, which was only a few days ago. I don’t understand how I could have booked a room much earlier than this and yet they are all gone already.\r\n\r\nYes please help me set up a reservation for the 27th-2nd. I have a reservation at a nearby hotel for the full stay, but if you can set me up for the 27th-2nd, I can change the hotel reservation to just the first two days (25th, 26th) and move over to Seminaris for the conference (since you are closer to the venue).\r\n\r\nLet’s set that up. Thank you.\r\n\r\n\r\nKeith Wiley\r\n\r\nsoftware engineer/ connectomics service engineer/\r\n\r\nkeith.wiley@alleninstitute.org\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[image.png]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you were not the intended recipient of this email, it may be confidential and you should immediately contact the sender and delete it.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFrom: Reservation - Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin <reservation.ber61@seminaris.com>\r\nDate: Friday, May 8, 2026 at 00:33\r\nTo: Keith Wiley <keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org>\r\nSubject: AW: Your request at Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin HRBSEBEBE23396477684\r\n\r\nCAUTION: This email originated from outside the Allen Institute. Please do not click links or open attachments unless you've validated the sender and know the content is safe.\r\n________________________________\r\nDear Mr Wiley\r\n\r\nThank you for your email.\r\n\r\nWe are fully booked on June 25th and 26th. We are happy to send you an offer with our daily rate for the period from June 27th to July 2nd.\r\n\r\nFor your information: A number of rooms were available at special rates for this event. All of these have now been booked already. That is why we can only offer you our standard daily rates.\r\n\r\nPlease do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or requests.\r\n\r\nKind regards\r\n\r\nMonique Fedtke\r\n\r\nReservation Agent\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSeminaris CampusHotel Berlin\r\n\r\nSeminaris Hotel- und Kongressstätten Betriebsgesellschaft mbH\r\n\r\nTakustraße 39, 14195 Berlin, Deutschland\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTelefonische Erreichbarkeit der Reservierung\r\n\r\nMo-Fr 09:00 bis 16:00\r\n\r\nT +49 30 557 797 0\r\n\r\nreservation.ber61@seminaris.com<mailto:reservation.pot62@seminaris.com>\r\n\r\nseminaris.de<https://www.seminaris.de/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFollow us: LinkedIn<https://www.linkedin.com/company/seminarishotels> | Facebook<https://www.facebook.com/seminaris.hotels> | Instagram<https://www.instagram.com/seminaris.hotels/> | Youtube<https://www.youtube.com/@seminarishotels7804> | Pinterest<https://de.pinterest.com/seminarishotels/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSitz Registered office: Takustraße 39, 14195 Berlin, Deutschland\r\nRegistergericht Commercial register: Amtsgericht Charlottenburg, HRB 182457 B\r\n\r\nUSt-IdNr. VAT ID: DE811 341 157\r\n\r\nGeschäftsführer Managing Director: Dirk Rehanek\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[cid:d5a23574-c935-46e9-94d3-51c34f783949]<https://www.seminaris.de/>\r\n\r\nImpressum Legal notice: seminaris.de/impressum<https://www.seminaris.de/impressum/>\r\nDatenschutz Privacy Policy: seminaris.de/datenschutz<https://www.seminaris.de/datenschutz/>\r\n\r\nConfidentiality Notice: If you are not the intended recipient of this email, please delete it and notify the sender.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n________________________________\r\nVon: Keith Wiley <keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org>\r\nGesendet: Donnerstag, 07. Mai 2026 16:42\r\nAn: Reservation - Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin <reservation.ber61@seminaris.com>\r\nBetreff: Re: Your request at Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin HRBSEBEBE23396477684\r\n\r\nI don't understand. Are you staying I can reserve a room for the 27th - 2nd? The email said you had availability those days but also said you wouldn't take any reservations for those dates.\r\n\r\nGet Outlook for Android<https://aka.ms/AAb9ysg>\r\n\r\n________________________________\r\nFrom: Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin <reservation.ber61@seminaris.com>\r\nSent: Thursday, May 7, 2026 4:35:25 AM\r\nTo: Keith Wiley <keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org>\r\nSubject: Your request at Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin HRBSEBEBE23396477684\r\n\r\nCAUTION: This email originated from outside the Allen Institute. Please do not click links or open attachments unless you've validated the sender and know the content is safe.\r\n________________________________\r\n[Logo]\r\n[Banner]\r\n\r\nDear Keith Wiley,\r\n\r\n\r\nthank you for your kind request and your interest in our Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin.\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease note that all rooms in the room block have already been booked. We are happy to send you a quote with our current daily rates. Unfortunately, we are already fully booked for 25 and 26 June.\r\n\r\nFor detailed information on your offer please scroll down:\r\n\r\nArrival: Saturday 27.06.2026\r\n\r\nDeparture: Thursday 02.07.2026 (5 nights)\r\n\r\nNumber of room(s): 1\r\n\r\nNumber of guest(s) per room:  1 Adult(s)\r\n\r\nPlease book the room by clicking on the button and confirming your details. Your privacy is important to us, and this ensures that your personal data is transmitted securely.\r\n\r\n[No picture available]\r\nStandard Room\r\n\r\nLet yourself sink into the king-size bed of our approximately 23 m² large, cozy Standard room and you immediately feel that you will sleep very well here. If you still like to get up again: there is also a large desk where you can work relaxed - but you don't have to!\r\n\r\nBest flexible Rate incl. parking\r\n\r\n• Including breakfast • Including parking space • Book now. Pay later.\r\n\r\n€ 170.40\r\nAvg. Price per room/night\r\n€ 852.00 Total per stay\r\nCancellations are free of charge until 6:00 p.m. on the day of arrival. For later cancellations of g...\r\nselect offer and review details<https://bookings.seminaris.de/108183?languageid=1&adults=1&dateIn=06/27/2026&dateOut=07/02/2026&roomtypeid=459845&rateplanid=9328560&rooms=1&email=keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org&referid=1851921521&utm_campaign=HRBSEBEBE23396477684&utm_source=HERA&utm_medium=Addin>\r\n\r\nBase Rate incl. breakfast\r\n\r\n• Including Breakfast • Book now. Pay later.\r\n\r\n€ 156.40\r\nAvg. Price per room/night\r\n€ 782.00 Total per stay\r\nCancellations are free of charge until 6:00 p.m. on the day of arrival. For later cancellations of g...\r\nselect offer and review details<https://bookings.seminaris.de/108183?languageid=1&adults=1&dateIn=06/27/2026&dateOut=07/02/2026&roomtypeid=459845&rateplanid=5005926&rooms=1&email=keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org&referid=1851921521&utm_campaign=HRBSEBEBE23396477684&utm_source=HERA&utm_medium=Addin>\r\n\r\nBEST DEAL incl. breakfast, non-refundable\r\n\r\n• Non-refundable rate • Including breakfast • 100% pre-payment\r\n\r\n€ 140.26\r\nAvg. Price per room/night\r\n€ 701.30 Total per stay\r\nCancellation is not possible free of charge. In case of cancellation or no-show, no refund will be g...\r\nselect offer and review details<https://bookings.seminaris.de/108183?languageid=1&adults=1&dateIn=06/27/2026&dateOut=07/02/2026&roomtypeid=459845&rateplanid=5005935&rooms=1&email=keith.wiley@alleninstitute.org&referid=1851921521&utm_campaign=HRBSEBEBE23396477684&utm_source=HERA&utm_medium=Addin>\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease be advised that currently we do not hold a reservation for the above quoted room(s).\r\n\r\nThere is no legal claim to the above-mentioned rooms and rates. Availability of rooms and rates are limited and subject to change any time.\r\n\r\nSEMINARIS CAMPUSHOTEL BERLIN-DAHLEM: FEELING THE HEARTBEAT OF THE CAPITAL CITY\r\n[Hotelpicture]\r\n\r\nAt the Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin, we combine all of this into a special hotel experience. Surrounded by green nature, you can sleep comfortably in 186 rooms, explore the city, breathe fresh air and enjoy a variety of cuisine. But most of all, you’ll experience extraordinary meetings and events that are sure to inspire you and provide you with new ideas. With its home on the campus of Freie Universität, Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin is located in a place that transforms a lot of knowledge into new goals and projects.\r\n\r\nRELAXED ENJOYMENT: RESTAURANT AND BAR IN BERLIN-DAHLEM\r\n[Restaurant]\r\n\r\nRestaurant Papillon. The menu at the Papillon restaurant is particularly varied, light and fresh. The kitchen team surprises again and again with exciting aromas and flavor combinations.\r\n\r\nFaculty Club Bar & Lounge. Good drinks are studied at this “faculty” in the Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin. Classic long drinks, finely tuned cocktails or cultivated wine bring well-deserved relaxation after an eventful day.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.\r\n\r\n\r\nWith kind regards,\r\n\r\n\r\nMonique Fedtke\r\n\r\nReservierung\r\n\r\n[Pin Icon]\r\n\r\nTakustraße 39 14195 Berlin\r\n\r\n[Telephone Icon]\r\n\r\n+49 30 557 797 0\r\n\r\nSeminaris CampusHotel Berlin | District court Berlin, Charlottenburg HRB 182457 B | Managing Director Dirk Rehanek Annelie Richers\r\n\r\nData Protection<https://www.seminaris.de/en/privacy/>\r\nTerms & Conditions<https://www.seminaris.de/en/terms/>\r\n\r\n© 2026 Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin\r\n\r\nHRBSEBEBE23396477684\r\n\r\nYour request:\r\n\r\nThursday 07.05.2026\r\nkeith.wiley@alleninstitute.org\r\n\r\nWG: Reservation form attached for June 25 - July 2, 2026. Thank you.\r\n\r\n\r\n________________________________\r\n\r\nVon: Keith Wiley\r\n\r\nGesendet: Mittwoch, 6. Mai 2026 18:48\r\n\r\nAn: Conference- Seminaris CampusHotel Berlin\r\n\r\nBetreff: Reservation form attached for June 25 - July 2, 2026. Thank you.\r\n\r\n\r\nReservation form attached for June 25 - July 2, 2026. Thank you."

